# Deploy Completed Changes

After implementing and verifying requested changes:

- Commit all relevant project changes.
- Push the current branch to its remote automatically.
- Do not include unrelated pre-existing changes or files containing secrets.
- If commit, push, CI, or deployment fails, report the blocker clearly.
